Oke, selanjutnya genre laga…

41
00:03:11,399 --> 00:03:12,233
Untuk ini…

42
00:03:12,317 --> 00:03:13,151
<i>Aku lengah.</i>

43
00:03:13,234 --> 00:03:14,152
Sial.

44
