Hei, tidak perlu.

77
00:04:27,392 --> 00:04:29,227
- Ketemu!
- Coba aku lihat.

78
00:04:29,727 --> 00:04:32,146
Wah, dia sangat ideal.

79
00:04:32,230 --> 00:04:34,440
Dia super oke!

80
