Astaga, justru aku suka pria lebih muda.

110
00:05:49,724 --> 00:05:51,976
Apa? Kalau begitu, mau kukenalkan?

111
00:05:53,061 --> 00:05:54,270
Kalau itu…

112
00:05:54,354 --> 00:05:56,105
Coba lihat fotonya lagi.

113
00:05:56,189 --> 00:05:57,023
Oke.

114
00:05:58,316 --> 00:06:00,610
- Dia tinggal di mana?
- Di Seoul.

115
00:06:00,693 --> 00:06:02,445
Kebetulan aku pun di Seoul.

116
00:06:02,528 --> 00:06:04,030
- Super oke, 'kan?
- Ya.

117
00:06:04,113 --> 00:06:06,824
Aku suka jika tinggal di Seoul.
Jaraknya dekat.

118
00:06:07,784 --> 00:06:09,035
<i>Dia benar-benar…</i>

119
