- Aku pamit.

127
00:06:27,095 --> 00:06:27,929
Hei, kalian.

128
00:06:28,012 --> 00:06:29,931
- Aku duluan, ya.
- Ya.

129
00:06:30,014 --> 00:06:31,140
Sampai jumpa.

130
00:06:36,437 --> 00:06:37,772
- Kau ke arah mana?
- Apa?

131
00:06:38,272 --> 00:06:40,233
Aku belum dapat taksi.

132
00:06:40,733 --> 00:06:43,152
Aku juga. Nanti juga dapat.

133
