147
00:07:24,735 --> 00:07:26,696
- Apa?
- Jadi satu tim denganku.

148
00:07:29,031 --> 00:07:30,491
Tidak, bukan begitu…

149
00:07:31,075 --> 00:07:33,578
Kalau begitu, kita tetap satu tim saja.

150
00:07:37,957 --> 00:07:39,167
Oh, itu ada taksi.

151
00:07:43,129 --> 00:07:45,006
Kau naik yang di depan saja.

152
00:07:46,632 --> 00:07:47,758
Apa tak masalah?

153
00:07:48,718 --> 00:07:49,552
Apanya?

154
00:07:51,721 --> 00:07:52,555
Kau tak naik?

155
00:07:53,389 --> 00:07:56,142
Baiklah. Kalau begitu,
selamat berakhir pekan.

156
00:07:56,225 --> 00:07:57,977
Ya, kau juga.

157
00:07:58,060 --> 00:07:59,270
Dinginnya!

158
00:08:03,691 --> 00:08:05,109
Halo, Pak. Ke Yongsan.

159
00:08:05,610 --> 00:08:07,487
- Aku tak ke sana.
- Apa?

160
00:08:08,237 --> 00:08:10,990
Ini taksi Incheon.
Seharusnya kau lihat dulu.

161
00:08:12,909 --> 00:08:14,076
Maaf.

162
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,457
INCHEON

163
00:08:20,958 --> 00:08:22,835
Apa-apaan dia itu?

164
00:08:23,544 --> 00:08:24,921
Seharusnya kasih tahu!

165
00:08:40,019 --> 00:08:42,063
Bisa-bisanya mengajak kerja sama.

166
00:08:42,146 --> 00:08:43,314
Konyol sekali.

167
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:52,365
PLANC

168
00:08:52,448 --> 00:08:53,783
PRIA UNTUK DIKENAL

169
00:08:53,866 --> 00:08:55,785
Dikejar terus. Aku jadi gelisah.

170
00:08:58,621 --> 00:09:00,581
<i>Cuci mata setelah baca </i>Pria Untuk Dikenal<i>.</i>

171
00:09:00,665 --> 00:09:02,500
<i>Yun Song menyogok? Kok jadi nomor satu?</i>

172
00:09:02,583 --> 00:09:04,627
<i>Hwany, Dewa Komik. PlanC adalah dewa!</i>

173
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:06,462
JI-YEON

174
00:09:07,046 --> 00:09:09,298
Hei. Ada apa malam-malam begini?

175
00:09:09,382 --> 00:09:11,676
<i>Kenapa tak ada jawaban di grup?</i>

176
00:09:13,094 --> 00:09:14,512
Aku tak lihat. Kenapa?

177
00:09:14,595 --> 00:09:16,430
- Tak lupa soal besok, 'kan?
<i>- Apa?</i>

178
00:09:17,223 --> 00:09:18,432
Syukuran rumah Da-yeong.

179
00:09:21,477 --> 00:09:22,311
Oh, iya.

180
00:09:22,895 --> 00:09:24,981
<i>Sudah kuduga akan begini.</i>

181
00:09:25,064 --> 00:09:26,232
Jangan lupa.

182
00:09:28,401 --> 00:09:29,443
Sampai besok.

183
00:09:33,823 --> 00:09:35,950
Astaga, aku harus beli apa?

184
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:41,414
Hei, lihat.

185
00:09:41,497 --> 00:09:43,332
Astaga!

186
00:09:43,416 --> 00:09:44,250
Manis sekali.

187
00:09:44,333 --> 00:09:46,627
- Silakan dicoba.
- Terima kasih.

188
00:09:46,711 --> 00:09:47,545
Permisi.

189
00:09:47,628 --> 00:09:49,338
Apa ada artis idola yang datang?

190
00:09:49,839 --> 00:09:53,134
Tidak. Ini antrean gerai
Boyfriend on Demand.

191
00:09:54,677 --> 00:09:56,429
NOMOR ANTREAN 454

192
00:10:01,642 --> 00:10:03,394
Mohon lebih cepat.

193
00:10:19,952 --> 00:10:21,120
Produser Seo?

194
00:10:21,621 --> 00:10:23,789
- Oh, ya. Halo.
- Halo.

195
00:10:24,373 --> 00:10:27,209
Kau datang ke gerai kami?
Semestinya kuambilkan tiket antrean.

196
00:10:27,877 --> 00:10:30,588
Tidak. Aku hanya kebetulan lewat.

197
00:10:30,671 --> 00:10:31,505
Oh, begitu?

198
00:10:32,131 --> 00:10:32,965
Ya.

199
00:10:33,466 --> 00:10:35,509
Tempat ini populer sekali.

200
00:10:35,593 --> 00:10:37,053
Ya, tidak main-main.

201
00:10:37,887 --> 00:10:41,265
Sepertinya gerai kami ini
yang penjualannya paling bagus.

202
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:44,644
Selamat, Pak Min.

203
00:10:45,144 --> 00:10:47,313
Ini berkat ulasan darimu.

204
00:10:47,396 --> 00:10:48,481
Semuanya lancar?

205
00:10:50,066 --> 00:10:51,942
- Apanya?
- Boyfriend on Demand.

206
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:57,198
Aku…

207
00:10:58,532 --> 00:10:59,867
Aku tak main lagi.

208
00:10:59,950 --> 00:11:01,952
Sejak itu, aku tak main lagi.

209
00:11:02,828 --> 00:11:03,704
Begitu?

210
00:11:04,205 --> 00:11:07,041
Dari ulasanmu,
kelihatannya kau sangat puas.

211
00:11:07,124 --> 00:11:08,417
Dapat hadiah perangkat juga.

212
00:11:08,501 --> 00:11:11,504
Kukira kau akan berlangganan
setelah ini dirilis.

213
00:11:12,588 --> 00:11:15,299
Terima kasih hadiahnya,
tapi aku sangat sibuk.

214
00:11:16,092 --> 00:11:18,469
Tapi Boyfriend on Demand jauh lebih baik

215
00:11:18,552 --> 00:11:20,054
dari dunia nyata, 'kan?

216
00:11:23,391 --> 00:11:26,102
Entahlah. Tetap saja
dunia nyata lebih baik.

217
00:11:27,395 --> 00:11:28,229
Kau tegas, ya.

218
00:11:28,854 --> 00:11:31,190
Mumpung di sini, ayo lihat-lihat dulu.

219
00:11:31,273 --> 00:11:33,651
- Akan kupandu.
- Tidak perlu.

220
00:11:33,734 --> 00:11:36,487
Aku ingin beli sesuatu,
jadi harus cepat pergi.

221
00:11:37,947 --> 00:11:40,282
Kalau begitu, sampai bertemu lagi.

222
00:11:40,366 --> 00:11:42,034
- Terima kasih.
- Semangat.

223
00:11:46,664 --> 00:11:47,832
Mengejutkan saja.

224
00:11:55,423 --> 00:11:56,257
Halo. Kenapa?

225
00:11:56,340 --> 00:11:58,092
<i>Kau tak lupa, 'kan?</i>

226
00:11:58,175 --> 00:11:59,552
Memangnya aku ikan mas?

227
00:11:59,635 --> 00:12:02,096
Tentu saja. Aku sedang membeli hadiah.

228
00:12:02,179 --> 00:12:03,681
Syukurlah.

229
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:06,183
Ada yang mau kubicarakan.

230
00:12:06,684 --> 00:12:07,518
<i>Mau bicara?</i>

231
00:12:08,018 --> 00:12:09,145
Jangan marah, ya.

232
00:12:09,228 --> 00:12:10,062
Ada apa?

233
00:12:10,563 --> 00:12:13,607
<i>Ada satu orang lagi</i>
<i>yang datang ke rumah Da-yeong.</i>

234
00:12:13,691 --> 00:12:14,525
Siapa?

235
00:12:14,608 --> 00:12:17,778
Dia cuma kenalannya Da-yeong.

236
00:12:18,779 --> 00:12:19,905
Mau dikenalkan kepadamu.

237
00:12:22,742 --> 00:12:23,576
<i>Halo?</i>

